Servlet::
	->Is a web-component,it resides on the server.it is one of the core components of Web-Application
	->Servlets are responsible for handling a web clients request,it will process the clients request 
		and generates a response dynamically and sends back to the client


In the servlet API we got two different classes
	---Generic Servlet Class(javax.servlet.GenericServlet)
	---Http Servlet class(javax.servlet.http.HttpServlet)
	
javax.servlet.GenericServlet
We have following method
	service()
		->We write Request Processing Code